c c c
lw(1i) lw(1i) lw(1i).
Format:Typical extension:Type of data
_
Gimp XCF:.xcf:Sprites and animations
WAVE file:.wav:Audio samples
Ogg Vorbis:.ogg:Music, large samples
MPEG-1 stream:.mpeg:Videos
.TE
.Ed
